  "instructions": [
    "preheat oven to 375\u000040f",
    "combine barley, mustard seeds, and dried thyme in a bowl",
    "in a pan, heat olive oil over medium heat, then add chopped onion and garlic, cooking until softened",
    "add lardons-render to the pan, stirring to combine",
    "transfer the barley mixture to a baking dish, top with the pan mixture, and cover with chopped kale",
    "bake for 20 minutes, or until the kale is tender and the flavors have melded together"
